1. http://jshint.com/ & http://jshint.com/about/
2. jshint configuration: http://jshint.com/docs/options/
3. sample .jshintrc file is stored under the folder from ka generator by JR
4. npm install -g jshint
5. for sumlime install JSHint plugin: https://github.com/uipoet/sublime-jshint
6. related static check tools: jscs - http://jscs.info/
7. use with grunt: https://github.com/gruntjs/grunt-contrib-jshint
